{"tid":178649,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲有/覺得自己有身體畸型恐懼症（BDD)？","createTime":"2017-03-29T16:24:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T20:59:19.000Z","uid":24615,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bb1763f55e5bdfde412678da9f8d5b215d565052","tid":178649,"uid":24615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T16:24:20.000Z","msg":"病徵：<br />\n1.覺得自己個樣/身體某d部位有缺陷，而呢個缺陷可能只係d小問題或者根本係正常範圍之內<br />\n例子：覺得自己個鼻唔夠高 覺得自己個頭太大 覺得自己二頭肌太瘦（但可能已經係健美先生level) 覺得自己手指太細等<br />\n<br />\n2.有d人當做完整容手術/皮膚護理等 都係覺得唔夠/問題轉移到另一個部位<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.病人低awareness。姐通常都唔覺得自己有病<br />\n<br />\n4.就算覺得自己有病，好多都寧願繼續受個病既折磨都唔想去被說服自己個樣其實冇問題<br />\n<br />\n病人會因為咁而自我價值低下 影響自信同社交<br />\n<br />\n感覺上呢到好多巴絲都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但講真 我學左咁耐都唔識分一個人 究竟係有呢個病定真係樣衰導致自我價值低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e4c1a927145427ad076c5ae678caca3273ce6a6","tid":178649,"uid":104793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T20:59:19.000Z","msg":"點算，我覺得自己可能有。<br />\n<a href=\"http://bddfoundation.org/helping-you/questionnaires/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbddfoundation.org%2Fhelping-you%2Fquestionnaires%2F&d=oGSqBYpvdEZZERTBUGrA0tWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=420dd53b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bddfoundation.org/helping-you/questionnaires/</a><br />\n2個questionnaires 6x/72, 3x/40"}]}